{"tid":1950441,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"終於諗通點解貧富懸殊係必然","createTime":"2020-03-30T10:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T12:48:15.000Z","uid":54930,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e45e43c84ae91bab30ae7c5ef5b3701fd9840beb","tid":1950441,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"假設有一班人個個都冇錢個個都窮<br />\n之後經濟慢慢開始發展,就有部份人先富起來,另一部份人繼續窮<br />\n社會就開始有貧富懸殊出現<br />\n但個社會只係有能力令一部份人富,冇能力令全部都人富<br />\n如果想令窮人變富人,社會只能犧牲富人,將佢地變返窮人<br />\n咁先有能力將其他窮人變返富人,直到佢再冇能力令更多人富起來,<br />\n於是又變返貧富懸殊<br />\n因為富人係要靠窮人令佢地變富,有富人就有窮人,但冇富人都有窮人<br />\n呢個就叫零和遊戲<br />\n結論<br />\n大家努力d返工搵錢,令自己變富人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貧富懸殊係必然,人人平等只係理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65b2a302a1e23f48588249ecb3d963cb99d654e","tid":1950441,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"如果你地一早知唔好笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我iq得130"},{"pid":"a6038b33ab4f94c5aa33d60a5ea0d83182cf0c71","tid":1950441,"uid":45753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"望下西歐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然你可以話100蚊同1000蚊都係貧富懸殊"},{"pid":"b0c6458d50711352eb054e493725f16ce96c4603","tid":1950441,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"所謂有能力咪又係錢搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226a7d7af6ed4b143493c4c08f58a61cbd0524bb","tid":1950441,"uid":350576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"你好似講緊啲人人都知嘅野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利：冇測過智商 做網上啲sup9測試得110<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73a6fec4996401ac25502b8bb61c1a558b13602","tid":1950441,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":